Rolls-Royce Plans South American Car Dealerships, Telegraph Says

-- B y   T h o m a s   B i e s h e u v e l
-- 
2011-10-23T07:35:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-23/rolls-royce-plans-south-american-car-dealerships-telegraph-says.html
Rolls-Royce Motor Cars is planning
to open dealerships in Brazil and  Chile  to widen its global
reach, the Sunday Telegraph reported, citing Chief Executive
Officer Torsten Mueller-Oetvoes.  Mueller-Oetvoes sees about 100 dealerships as the right
number to have globally, the Telegraph said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Thomas Biesheuvel in  London  at 
 tbiesheuvel@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Viljoen at 
 jviljoen@bloomberg.net  